{"tid":986704,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[最有升班相係?]#林泳淘 湯怡 黃智雯 陳嘉寶 袁澧林 劉穎鏇 18-19 LIHKG香港冠軍女神聯賽第十九輪投選專區","createTime":"2019-01-18T16:29:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T22:55:30.000Z","uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"be5cccaa5ff298198a8b9d99e393829c20fecb06","tid":986704,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T16:29:30.000Z","msg":"以下為即將舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可留意稍後時間發出的比賽專用回覆並以回覆評分功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(唔識點樣用回覆評分功能黎投票既巴打可以參考下面既教學)<br />\n<br />\n由首場12:30am開始,每兩分鐘開賽一場<br />\n<br />\n趙慧珊@SG : 陳煒<br />\n黃心穎 : 黃智雯<br />\n黃翠如 : 陳嘉寶<br />\n莊錠欣 : 彭慧中<br />\n游蕙禎 : 劉穎鏇<br />\n袁澧林 : 朱晨麗<br />\n林泳淘 : 湯怡<br />\n岑麗香 : 陳庭欣<br />\n李施嬅 : 孫慧雪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hiNda68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhiNda68.png&h=d4221617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s2sfX8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs2sfX8L.png&h=b53ffa65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冠聯第十八輪積分榜<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/4dIX043.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F4dIX043.png&h=ed52c52b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/fg4vwe7.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ffg4vwe7.png&d=o08bY4dqXQVq3GKoAj2E%2B10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=8b5ff6b1\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/fg4vwe7.png</a><br />\n有關主場指定額外得分情況,請參閱主場額外分數增幅表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df72d778c2f43b5068e48014ea6df9fa0882721","tid":986704,"uid":92376,"like":68,"dislike":93,"score":-25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T16:30:02.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-19 LIHKG香港冠軍女神聯賽第十九輪</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">*括號內數字為聯賽排名</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2019-1-19 12:30am-10:30pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/lwC8bpm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FlwC8bpm.png&h=341d4147&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hJcEIZ2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhJcEIZ2.png&h=6c079671&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(13)趙慧珊@SGvs陳煒(10)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"e24e73635f34dbc1b6332ff1d9c2e050a7ec3d52","tid":986704,"uid":92376,"like":23,"dislike":138,"score":-115,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T16:32:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2019-1-19 12:32am-10:32pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/oaghC9X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FoaghC9X.png&h=2094a093&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/UOt9IER.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FUOt9IER.png&h=422ef8d1&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(18)黃心穎vs黃智雯(6)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"0ac88478606d92188846b905375c3e7902fc6a8a","tid":986704,"uid":92376,"like":62,"dislike":93,"scor